      <h1 class='title'>Intelligence Services Commissioner</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 21 March 2003 vol 401 c57WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_57ws' title='Col. 57WS &mdash; HC Deb 21 March 2003 vol 401 c57WS' name='column_57ws' href='#column_57ws' rel='bookmark'>57WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0401P0-05128'>
        <a name='S6CV0401P0_20030321_CWS_2'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-tony-blair' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0401P0_20030321_CWS_2' title='Link to this speech by Mr Tony Blair' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-tony-blair" title="Mr Tony Blair">The Prime Minister (Mr. Tony Blair)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0401P0-05128">In accordance with Section 59(1) of the <a href="/acts/regulation-of-investigatory-powers-act-2000">Regulation of Investigatory Powers Act 2000</a>, after consultation with the Foreign, Home and Defence Secretaries, I have decided to reappoint Lord Justice Simon Brown as the Intelligence Services Commissioner from 1 April 2003 to 31 March 2006.</p><p id="S6CV0401P0-05129">I am delighted that Lord Justice Simon Brown has agreed to continue to serve as the Intelligence Services Commissioner.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
